job.title: BPSC Asst. Audit Officer  Recruitment 2021 –  Apply Online for 138 Vacancies in Bihar
job.body:
Total Vacancies:138

Name of the post:

  • Assistant Audit Officer (Bihar Audit Services) 

Description:

Bihar Public Service Commission (BPSC)  issued a total of 138 vacancies for the posts of Assistant Audit Officer (Bihar Audit Services)  . The online application for these posts under BPSC shall start from 17-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 29-06-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for BPSC Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for Gen/ Other: Rs.600/-
  • The application fee for SC/ ST & Women of Bihar State: Rs. 150/-
  • The application fee for PWD Candidates: Rs. 150/-
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 17-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 29-06-2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have a Bachelor Degree (Commerce, Economics, Statistics & Mathematics)/ MBA (Fiance), CA, ICWA, CS to apply for the post of Assistant Audit Officer (Bihar Audit Services) 

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is: 21 years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 42 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Assistant Audit Officer (Bihar Audit Services) is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that BPSC issued this notification for which posts.

  •  Assistant Audit Officer - 138

How to apply for BPSC Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of BPSC
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Assistant Audit Officer (Bihar Audit Services) 
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
